OL,3,CWoman denies charges relating to young
OL,4,Cmum's murder
OL,6,FA woman has denied charges relating to
OL,7,Fthe fatal shooting of a young mother
OL,8,Fin Sheffield after the man accused of
OL,9,Fher murder failed to appear in court.
OL,11,FDeiryen Dyce, 32, faces a number of
OL,12,Fcharges following the investigation
OL,13,Finto the attack on 30-year-old Shanice
OL,14,FBrookes in Sheffield on 25 May.
OL,16,FShe denied assisting an offender and
OL,17,Fpossessing ammunition as well as drugs
OL,18,Fcharges when she appeared at Sheffield
OL,19,FCrown Court on Monday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
