OL,3,CWoman denies charges relating to young
OL,4,Cmum's murder
OL,6,FDyce, of Ellesmere Road North,
OL,7,FSheffield, was remanded in custody
OL,8,Funtil a pre-trial review on a date to
OL,9,Fbe fixed in November, ahead of a trial
OL,10,Fdue to begin in January next year.
OL,12,FJemele Rhone, 30, is charged with
OL,13,Fmurdering mother-of-one Ms Brookes,
OL,14,Fwho was an innocent bystander when she
OL,15,Fwas shot near the One Four One bar in
OL,16,FWest Street, in the city centre,
OL,17,Fshortly before 2.45am.
OL,19,FRhone, of Outram Road, Sheffield, who
OL,20,Fis remanded in custody, failed to
OL,21,Fattend Monday's hearing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
