OL,3,CWoman denies charges relating to young
OL,4,Cmum's murder
OL,6,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC ordered him
OL,7,Fto appear at a hearing at the same
OL,8,Fcourt on 20 July.
OL,10,FHe set a trial date of 18 January next
OL,11,Fyear, pushing back by two weeks a
OL,12,Fprovisional date of 4 January.
OL,14,FThe judge said the time estimate for
OL,15,Fthe trial, to be heard by a High Court
OL,16,Fjudge, is three weeks.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
