OL,3,CWoman denies charges relating to young
OL,4,Cmum's murder
OL,6,FAt an earlier magistrates' court
OL,7,Fhearing, prosecutors described the
OL,8,Fincident as an "alleged street
OL,9,Fshooting" and said Ms Brookes was an
OL,10,F"entirely innocent bystander".
